subject: Dakar Rally
Motorcycles, Motor Bikes and Motorscooters
Automobile Racing
lead_paragraph: The Frenchmen Stephane Peterhansel and Cyril Despres have defended their car and motorbike titles in the Dakar Rally, which moved to South America from Africa in 2009 for security reasons.
